foia:Exemption3StatuteSection.foia:FootnoteText: The MSPB did not rely on Exemption 3 to withhold any records. Consequently, MSPB reports no court decisions involving Exemption 3 determinations.

foia:RequestDenialOtherReasonSection.foia:FootnoteText: The MSPB did not deny any requests based on "Other" reasons not already described above

foia:OldestPendingAppealSection.foia:FootnoteText: The MSPB did not have any pending adminstrative appeals at the end of FY 2010.

foia:ProcessedResponseTimeSection.foia:FootnoteText: Although MSPB received requests for expedited processing, all such requests routinely were processed within 5 day of receipt. Therefore, we did not rule on any requests for expedited processing.

foia:SimpleResponseTimeIncrementsSection.foia:FootnoteText: During FY 2010, MSPB received numerous FOIA requests that were delayed for various reasons, e.g., we requested relevant records from Federal Records Center and MSPB regional and field offices, and many records were sent to our copying contractor. In other instances, MSPB first generated reports to identify responsive documents. Upon receipt of those records, we reviewed them for appropriate redaction under one of the FOIA Exemptions. Many of the records contained 2,700 pages or more. However, on an ongoing basis MSPB contacted requesters whose responses were delayed, and we did not receive any complaints regarding our efforts to respond.

foia:ComplexResponseTimeIncrementsSectio.foia:FootnoteText: Table not applicable. The MSPB does not use multi-track processing. All MSPB FOIA requests are included in the table above ("Simple Requests").

foia:ExpeditedResponseTimeIncrementsSect.foia:FootnoteText: Table not applicable. The MSPB did not rule on any requests for expedited processing.

foia:ExpeditedProcessingSection.foia:FootnoteText: Table not applicable. The MSPB did not rule on any requests for expedited processing

foia:ProcessedConsultationSection.foia:FootnoteText: The MSPB did not receive any requests for consultations during FY 2010.

foia:OldestPendingConsultationSection.foia:FootnoteText: The MSPB did not have any pending consultations on FOIA requests at the end of FY 2010.
